{
  "id": "69af3febf8ca9cc4459f156d",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:人物関係図",
  "created": 1773092868,
  "updated": 1773578857,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69af3febf8ca9cc4459f156d",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:人物関係図",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092868,
      "updated": 1773092868
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400300000000003b5c59",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092868,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c5a",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも、今日は「[人物関係図]」について話すってことで集まったんだけどさ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773578857
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c5b",
      "text": "マンガとかアニメ見てると、よく公式サイトにあるじゃん？ あの「誰が誰とどういう関係」みたいな図。あれってマジ便利じゃね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c5d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c5e",
      "text": "ええ、確かにそうですね。物語の登場人物たちは、まるで糸で結ばれた星々のように、互いに関係を結びながら物語を形づくりますもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c5f",
      "text": "人物関係図は、その星座をひと目で眺めるための地図のようなもの…そう思うと、なんだか趣深いですね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c60",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c61",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c62",
      "text": "概ね同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c63",
      "text": "人物関係図は、登場人物間の関係を可視化したグラフ構造。ノード（人物）とエッジ（関係）で構成される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c65",
      "text": "グラフ理論の基礎概念に近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c66",
      "text": "参考: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graph_theory",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c68",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c69",
      "text": "出た、りかの理系ワードｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c6a",
      "text": "でもつまり、キャラ＝点、関係＝線ってことだよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c6c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c6d",
      "text": "その理解で正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c6e",
      "text": "例えば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c6f",
      "text": " 友人関係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c70",
      "text": " 家族関係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c71",
      "text": " 敵対関係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c73",
      "text": "こういった関係タイプをエッジの属性として付与する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c74",
      "text": "するとストーリー構造が整理される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c75",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c76",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c77",
      "text": "なるほど…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c78",
      "text": "人と人とのつながりを、糸で結ぶように描くのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c7a",
      "text": "物語を読むとき、私はときどき登場人物が増えると迷子になってしまうのですが、関係図があると安心して読み進められる気がします。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c7c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c7d",
      "text": "それなー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c7e",
      "text": "とくに群像劇とかヤバいよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c80",
      "text": "「この人誰だっけ？」ってなって、Wikiとか公式サイトで人物相関図チェック勢になるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c82",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c83",
      "text": "群像劇はネットワーク密度が高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c84",
      "text": "つまり人物間のエッジ数が多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c85",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c86",
      "text": "そのため、関係図の価値が上がる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c87",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c88",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c89",
      "text": "おお…なんかゲームのスキルツリーみたいだな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c8a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c8b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c8c",
      "text": "近い概念。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c8d",
      "text": "実際、関係性をゲームシステムとして扱う作品もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c8f",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c90",
      "text": " ソーシャルリンク（ペルソナシリーズ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c91",
      "text": " 好感度システム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c92",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c93",
      "text": "プレイヤーとキャラの関係もグラフの一部になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c95",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c96",
      "text": "人との関係が、物語の中で育っていくのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c97",
      "text": "まるで庭の花が、少しずつ咲いてゆくように。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c99",
      "text": "友情が深まったり、誤解が解けたり…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c9a",
      "text": "そうした変化が、物語の温度になるのだと思います。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c9c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c9d",
      "text": "あや、表現が文学すぎて草…いや尊い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5c9f",
      "text": "でも確かにさ、人物関係図って最初と最後で変わるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca0",
      "text": "敵だったやつが味方になったり、友達がライバルになったり。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca3",
      "text": "それは関係状態の遷移。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca5",
      "text": "時系列で見ると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca6",
      "text": "静的図ではなくダイナミックネットワークになる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca8",
      "text": "社会ネットワーク分析でも研究されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ca9",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_network_analysis",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5caa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cab",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cac",
      "text": "うわ、急に論文感ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cae",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5caf",
      "text": "けれど、面白い考え方ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb0",
      "text": "人と人との関係が、時間とともに形を変える…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb2",
      "text": "それを図にすると、物語の流れそのものが見えてくるのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb5",
      "text": "つまりさ、まとめるとこんな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb6",
      "text": " 人物関係図＝キャラのつながりを見える化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb7",
      "text": " キャラ＝点",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb8",
      "text": " 関係＝線",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cb9",
      "text": " 物語が進むと関係も変わる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cba",
      "text": "って感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cbb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cbc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cbd",
      "text": "概念整理として妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cbe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cbf",
      "text": "さらに言うと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc0",
      "text": "複雑な物語ほど人物関係図の価値が高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc2",
      "text": "理解コストを下げるツールになる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc4",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc5",
      "text": "読者にとっての道しるべ、なのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc6",
      "text": "たくさんの人物が織りなす物語でも、迷わず歩いていけるように…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc8",
      "text": "人物関係図は、物語の森に立つ案内板のようなものかもしれません。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cc9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cca",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ccb",
      "text": "おお〜いい締め！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ccc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ccd",
      "text": "じゃあ今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cce",
      "text": "人物関係図＝物語の人間ネットワークを見える化する地図！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5ccf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd0",
      "text": "マンガでも小説でもゲームでも、あるとめっちゃ助かる神ツールってわけ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd2",
      "text": "りかの理系解説と、あやの文学エモで、いい感じに理解できた気がするわｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd4",
      "text": "また次のテーマもやろーぜ！ 🎮📚💻",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
      "id": "69af400500000000003b5cd6",
      "text": "#2026-03-10",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773092869,
      "updated": 1773092869
    },
    {
